plot: Stay-at-home mom Kim is driving everyone crazy with her judgmental attitude! Sick of being constantly picked on, Kourtney and Khloe get crafty and plot nasty revenge on Kim. But her sisters aren't the only ones fed up with her, as Kris has had enough of Kim's complete takeover of her home. Especially when she finds out Kim's house is not even close to being ready! But all is forgotten when Kris gets a phone call about Kanye's surprise "birthday plans" for Kim and the family in San Francisco!—Anonymous
